data.description: Here's it is!  This PRE-INSPECTED 3 Bed 3 Bath multi level home in the Millard school district is waiting for you . The home features vaulted ceilings in front entry,  kitchen and living room.  The kitchen is open with a pantry, tile backsplash and laminate flooring.  Lots of natural light come through the bay window in living room and skylight in the main bath.  The primary bedroom has a 3/4 bath, and lower level family room with 1/2 bath.  HVAC 2022  Exterior features are vinyl siding, newer windows, new roof in 2019,  the  Backyard is fenced with a full privacy fence, shed, playset, patio, lots of landscaping and even a chicken coop. (sellers will remove if buyer does not want)  Close to Lake Zorinsky, parks, walking trails, schools and shopping. Schedule your showing today!
